#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:2
msgid "Model Context Protocol (MCP) — Ticket Server"
msgstr "模型上下文协议（MCP）——工单服务"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:5
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:7
msgid ""
"Loonflow exposes a **Model Context Protocol** server that lets compatible"
" clients (for example AI-assisted editors) query and handle tickets "
"through authenticated tools. The server name advertised to clients is "
"``loonflow-ticket``. Tools call the same permission-aware ticket services"
" as the web UI."
msgstr ""
"Loonflow 提供 **模型上下文协议（Model Context Protocol）** 服务端点，使兼容的客户端（例如带 AI "
"能力的编辑器）在通过认证后查询与处理工单。对客户端展示的服务名称为 ``loonflow-ticket``。工具内部调用与 Web "
"界面一致的、带权限校验的工单服务。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:10
msgid "Authentication"
msgstr "认证方式"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:12
msgid ""
"Calls must be authenticated with an **access token**. Supported token "
"types include:"
msgstr "调用必须使用 **访问令牌（access token）** 进行认证。支持的令牌类型包括："

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:14
msgid ""
"**Personal access token** (recommended for MCP clients): values start "
"with ``lfpat.``"
msgstr "**个人访问令牌（Personal access token）**（推荐用于 MCP 客户端）：值以 ``lfpat.`` 开头"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:15
msgid "**JWT** issued by Loonflow (same as API usage)"
msgstr "由 Loonflow 签发的 **JWT**（与 API 用法相同）"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:17
msgid ""
"You can pass the token in the MCP HTTP client as a header (see "
"configuration below), pass it per tool where supported, or configure a "
"server-side environment variable for non-interactive setups."
msgstr "你可以在 MCP 的 HTTP 客户端中以请求头传递令牌（见下文配置）、在支持的工具参数中传入，或在无人值守场景下通过服务端环境变量配置。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:20
msgid "Create a personal access token"
msgstr "创建个人访问令牌"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:22
msgid ""
"Open **Personal Information** in the product UI, then open **Personal "
"Access Token**. Create a new token and store it securely. Replace ``xxx``"
" in the configuration example with that token."
msgstr ""
"在产品界面进入 **个人信息（Personal Information）**，再进入 **个人访问令牌（Personal Access "
"Token）**。新建令牌并妥善保存，将配置示例中的 ``xxx`` 替换为该令牌。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:25
msgid "Personal Information and Personal Access Token in Loonflow"
msgstr "Loonflow 中的个人信息与个人访问令牌"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:29
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**Screenshot slot 1:** Navigate to Personal Information → Personal Access"
" Token (add ``mcp_profile_personal_access_token.png``)."
msgstr "导航至 个人信息 → 个人访问令牌。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:31
msgid "Create personal access token dialog or form"
msgstr "创建个人访问令牌的对话框或表单"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:35
msgid ""
"**Screenshot slot 2:** Create or manage personal access tokens (add "
"``mcp_create_personal_access_token.png``)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:38
msgid "Client configuration (example)"
msgstr "客户端配置（示例）"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:40
msgid ""
"Use the Streamable HTTP endpoint exposed by the MCP process (default path"
" ``/mcp``). Adjust host and port to match your deployment; local "
"development often uses port ``8002``."
msgstr ""
"使用 MCP 进程提供的 Streamable HTTP 端点（默认路径 ``/mcp``）。请按实际部署修改主机与端口；本地开发常见端口为 "
"``8002``。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:42
msgid ""
"For the Loonflow SaaS service, use ``https://mcp.loonflow.com/mcp`` as "
"the MCP server URL."
msgstr "对于 Loonflow SaaS 服务，请使用 ``https://mcp.loonflow.com/mcp`` 作为 MCP 服务地址。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:57
msgid ""
"Replace ``xxx`` with your **personal access token**. If the client "
"supports separate auth configuration, you may alternatively send ``X"
"-Loonflow-Access-Token`` with the raw token value."
msgstr ""
"将 ``xxx`` 替换为你的 **个人访问令牌**。若客户端支持单独配置认证信息，也可改用请求头 ``X-Loonflow-Access-"
"Token`` 传入原始令牌值。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:60
msgid "Supported tools"
msgstr "当前提供的 MCP 工具"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:62
msgid "The server currently registers the following tools."
msgstr "当前服务端注册如下工具。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:65
msgid "``ticket_list``"
msgstr "``ticket_list``"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:67
msgid ""
"Returns a **paginated ticket list** for the authenticated user, including"
" total count and pagination metadata."
msgstr "返回当前认证用户的 **分页工单列表**，包含总数与分页元数据。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:69 ../../source/mcp/index.rst:90
msgid "**Main behavior:**"
msgstr "**主要行为：**"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:71
msgid ""
"**category** selects which list to query: ``duty`` (my todo), ``owner`` "
"(created by me), ``relation`` (related to me), ``view`` (I can view), "
"``worked`` (tickets I processed), ``intervene`` (I can intervene), "
"``all`` (all tickets; **admin only**)."
msgstr ""
"**category** "
"选择列表类型：``duty``（我的待办）、``owner``（我创建的）、``relation``（与我相关的）、``view``（我可查看的）、``worked``（我处理过的）、``intervene``（我可干预的）、``all``（全部工单；**仅管理员**）。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:72
msgid ""
"Optional filters include free-text **search_value**, **create_start** / "
"**create_end**, **workflow_ids**, **node_ids**, **ticket_ids**, "
"**act_state**, **creator_id**, **parent_ticket_id**, **reverse**, "
"**per_page**, and **page**."
msgstr ""
"可选筛选包括全文 **search_value**、**create_start** / "
"**create_end**、**workflow_ids**、**node_ids**、**ticket_ids**、**act_state**、**creator_id**、**parent_ticket_id**、**reverse**、**per_page**、**page**"
" 等。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:73
msgid ""
"If neither ``create_start`` nor ``create_end`` is set, a default time "
"window is applied (see server implementation)."
msgstr "若未设置 ``create_start`` 与 ``create_end``，将应用默认时间范围（详见服务端实现）。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:76
msgid "``ticket_detail``"
msgstr "``ticket_detail``"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:78
msgid ""
"Loads **ticket detail** for a given ``ticket_id``: dynamic form schema "
"(**component_info_list**), workflow metadata, **field_permissions**, "
"derived **required_fields** / **optional_fields** / **readonly_fields**, "
"and available **actions** (plus **admin_actions** when applicable), "
"including base node identifiers used by some actions."
msgstr ""
"根据 ``ticket_id`` 加载 "
"**工单详情**：动态表单结构（**component_info_list**）、流程元数据、**field_permissions**，以及派生的"
" **required_fields** / **optional_fields** / **readonly_fields**，并返回可用 "
"**actions**（在适用时包含 **admin_actions**），其中含部分操作所需的基准节点标识。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:81
msgid "``ticket_prepare_handle``"
msgstr "``ticket_prepare_handle``"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:83
msgid ""
"Prepares the **same context as ticket detail** (form schema, permissions,"
" and available actions). Use it when you want a dedicated “prepare to "
"handle” step before submitting an action."
msgstr ""
"准备与 **ticket_detail** "
"相同的上下文（表单结构、字段权限与可用操作）。若希望在提交动作前先单独执行“准备处理”步骤，可使用本工具。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:86
msgid "``ticket_handle``"
msgstr "``ticket_handle``"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:88
msgid ""
"**Executes a workflow action** on a ticket after permission and field "
"validation."
msgstr "在通过权限与必填字段校验后，对工单 **执行流程动作**。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:92
msgid ""
"**action_type** and **action_id** must match one of the actions returned "
"for the current user (including admin actions when allowed)."
msgstr "**action_type** 与 **action_id** 必须与当前用户可用的动作之一一致（在允许时包含管理员动作）。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:93
msgid "**fields** must satisfy **required** fields for the current node/form."
msgstr "**fields** 必须满足当前节点/表单下的 **必填** 字段。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:94
msgid ""
"**action_props** carries extra properties required by specific actions "
"(for example node context for comments when applicable)."
msgstr "**action_props** 承载特定动作所需的附加属性（例如在适用时为评论类动作提供节点上下文）。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:95
msgid ""
"**dry_run**: when ``true``, validates the request and returns a summary "
"**without** changing the ticket; when ``false``, performs the handle "
"operation."
msgstr "**dry_run**：为 ``true`` 时仅校验请求并返回摘要，**不会**修改工单；为 ``false`` 时执行实际处理。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:98
msgid "Operational notes"
msgstr "运维说明"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:100
msgid ""
"Default listen address and port are controlled by environment variables "
"(for example ``LOONFLOW_MCP_HOST``, ``LOONFLOW_MCP_PORT``); align your "
"client URL with the running process."
msgstr ""
"默认监听地址与端口由环境变量控制（例如 ``LOONFLOW_MCP_HOST``、``LOONFLOW_MCP_PORT``）；请使客户端 "
"URL 与实际进程一致。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:101
msgid ""
"For server-side default authentication (for example stdio transports), "
"refer to ``LOONFLOW_MCP_ACCESS_TOKEN`` in the MCP server documentation in"
" the codebase."
msgstr ""
"若需在服务端配置默认认证（例如 stdio 传输），请参阅代码库中 MCP 服务器文档里的 "
"``LOONFLOW_MCP_ACCESS_TOKEN``。"

